{"tid":1167323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"等紅綠燈拍黃色盒仔","createTime":"2019-05-23T03:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T04:26:52.000Z","uid":7927,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"348cfbd5b69aec869b3e2a561e3cbeae2f95628e","tid":1167323,"uid":7927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:30:27.000Z","msg":"都唔係第一日嘅事 好多人等紅綠燈果陣都會拍個黃色盒等佢快啲轉綠燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌 但唔係個個黃色盒都有用 究竟啲人識唔識分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CjK2Eo3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCjK2Eo3.png&h=e0abe5b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n得呢隻有紅色燈罩嘅 拍左先有加速轉燈嘅作用 同埋拍完係會著紅燈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bpX0q4o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbpX0q4o.png&h=8ee42147&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢隻全黃色嘅係對一般人冇撚用！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拍19幾下都唔會快啲轉綠燈 <br />\n<br />\n佢係比盲人分辨紅綠燈用 紅燈會震得好慢 綠燈就震得好快 。同埋佢會根據環境嘈音聲量去調整紅綠燈嘅音量<br />\n<br />\n每次見到啲人起勢咁拍 佢個人又燥咁 真係好撚好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有啲仲係咁篤盒仔個底個制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好污漕"},{"pid":"e1955833c9fd6377c395aff62f0fc3aa132b3149","tid":1167323,"uid":7927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:39:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de7472078f73f2130762c708feebe546b39dad4","tid":1167323,"uid":41157,"